<h1 id="piluf-rice">Piluf (rice)</h1>

<h4 id="nice-rice">Nice rice.</h4>

<ul>
  <li>1 mug of rice</li>
  <li>2 mugs cold water</li>
  <li>Salt to taste</li>
  <li>Onion <em>finely chopped</em></li>
  <li>Olive oil</li>
  <li>Pinch of spagetti</li>
  <li>2 tbsp water</li>
</ul>

<ol>
  <li>
    <p>Fry the onion until soft.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Add the rice and stirfry for 3 minutes.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Add the water, bring to the boil. - add the salt, taste the water as you add salt
don't make it too salty but it needs to be well seasoned.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Turn the heat down and cover. It is cooked when all the water is gone. 15 - 20 minutes.</p>
  </li>
</ol>
